<% govspeak_for :body do %>
  <% if calculator.country == "bermuda" || calculator.country == "mauritius" %>
    You may be able to export Widowed Parent's Allowance to <%= calculator.country_name %>.

    Claim [Widowed Parent’s Allowance](/widowed-parents-allowance#how-to-claim) before you leave the UK.

    Once you have claimed bereavement benefits, contact the International Pension Centre to find out if you can export them.
  <% elsif calculator.country == "canada" %>
    You may be able to export bereavement benefits to <%= calculator.country_name %>.

    Claim [Bereavement Support Payment](/bereavement-support-payment/how-to-claim) before you leave the UK.

    Once you have claimed bereavement benefits, [contact the International Pension Centre](/international-pension-centre) to find out if you can export them.
  <% else %>
    You may be able to export bereavement benefits to <%= calculator.country_name %>.

    Claim [Bereavement Support Payment](/bereavement-support-payment/how-to-claim) or [Widowed Parent’s Allowance](/widowed-parents-allowance#how-to-claim) before you leave the UK.

    Once you have claimed bereavement benefits, [contact the International Pension Centre](/international-pension-centre) to find out if you can export them.
  <% end %>
<% end %>
